彩一刻唔可以錯過。<br />\n<br />\n我都知我好廢無當場反枱仲比錢佢賺，但係當時我一個女人佢地幾個阿叔可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心痛出去搏命嘅義士比佢地不停話，唯一做到只有公開佢，比大家思考下仲要唔要幫襯，我呢世都唔會再入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，佢啲麵都幾撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華富村華安樓地下投注站側邊嗰間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"呢檔野之前做走鬼檔，個肥仔有次屌到食環個個星期來掃場先租鋪做<br />\n<br />\n肥仔係呢區都出名吸毒食大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"我知佢以前車仔檔，反而嗰時都ok，宜家差左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講過個肥仔唔知咩黑社會成員黎"},{"pid":"0951e163686c71ff05447d7915c0e0c37237a3e9","tid":1505212,"uid":191701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"以前商場個邊擺檔之後不知係咪同房署deal 成 入鋪"},{"pid":"33183032e915bcdee4d652328b97347829e26416","tid":1505212,"uid":44929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"黑社會開架 藍到仆街"},{"pid":"8c76f9ffb04166eb6e19199d9df46a8867ec4119","tid":1505212,"uid":35758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾就算鳩數<br />\n食過一次永久blacklist<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e63fc3284e01d3e5b54160422b9077b014e75d","tid":1505212,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"南區仲有無車仔麵食得過?<br />\n<br />\n永發同拱照都藍, 仲有邊間食得過?"},{"pid":"0f4fa2bfbc27e4d722c686d1012942526aa278f5","tid":1505212,"uid":131017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e63fc3284e01d3e5b54160422b9077b014e75d","tid":1505212,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"南區仲有無車仔麵食得過?<br />\n<br />\n永發同拱照都藍, 仲有邊間食得過?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"見到舊街開左間榮記，未入過去唔知咩料"},{"pid":"839af66cdd353dfe461f3ca33fc7cee450f2f502","tid":1505212,"uid":8435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"呢間真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個死肥仔見足佢咁多年都係on99咁"},{"pid":"82349cc7b4eee4ac0766efc68d086b9a2f474c8a","tid":1505212,"uid":274037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"佢地平時成日講鄉下話架, 深藍黎"},{"pid":"153abf62b56393d9df920785d1dc6e3562be859d","tid":1505212,"uid":274037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"成家住華安架"},{"pid":"89912bc2719998b580c41d99034df7e959d04e94","tid":1505212,"uid":301360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c76f9ffb04166eb6e19199d9df46a8867ec4119","tid":1505212,"uid":35758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾就算鳩數<br />\n食過一次永久blacklist<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e1630fc8087b8d8c82e8a0636e1ca99d41cc96","tid":1505212,"uid":178791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:04:05.000Z","msg":"pish <br />\n唔食!"},{"pid":"84f99b84f90eae6425426179cec00df74d4b593d","tid":1505212,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"有無食環巴打去搞搞佢"},{"pid":"1e37d0d176fe81aca953942e52e7b2a42d954035","tid":1505212,"uid":77691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"個肥仔以前讀培英, 個樣成碌柒咁<br />\n以為自己好撚型果d 白撚痴來"},{"pid":"0fb9c163d8d6dde133df921d2f57d77fceb28581","tid":1505212,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"如果巴打真係想佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩每日都去<img src=\"