9T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"差過醫管局餐"},{"pid":"2b865b13ce2e9c64841103fd85e22bb7ae8bd742","tid":1505212,"uid":246118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41e63fc3284e01d3e5b54160422b9077b014e75d","tid":1505212,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"南區仲有無車仔麵食得過?<br />\n<br />\n永發同拱照都藍, 仲有邊間食得過?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:40:41.000Z","msg":"拱照正一死仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b86e89242dfee78667cd450a929fcfb799517b8","tid":1505212,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a4da0088c880284cad7b9ebc2e8bebd628de1e","tid":1505212,"uid":35758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c3abd1461bc704ec659d4ee9cac6249e6204806","tid":1505212,"uid":258893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"華富係深籃老人邨，後生既搬走哂。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"係深藍民主黨就唔會喺二邨做到成20年<br />\n下邨上次都係差少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:44:10.000Z","msg":"但個個黃才立好9架，一到選舉就扮曬日日落區<br />\n我驚下屆柴文翰輸，上次佢地2個票數好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb8f7daeaf0161036843024dc61845bf35c41a9","tid":1505212,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"佢之前有個大左肚既女人，應該係佢老婆應該仲係雙程證係到收錢，係咪報得入境"},{"pid":"e672430ba542c78c52e346d9373b29c5099977b9","tid":1505212,"uid":159760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24f77f1743769d51dcc6ada8d9344456d8e1d14","tid":1505212,"uid":131017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"我唔係住華富，唔知華富多傾向咩色，都唔知間野平時多唔多人食，不過望落幾污糟就真。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhaiWOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhaiWOF.jpg&h=f3f82f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，今日下午路經華富入去食碗粉，佢地電視播緊32台，麵檔阿姐喺度講佢唔了解發生緊咩事，不過認為次次咁多人抗爭應該係有大件事先咁多人堅持搏命出去，去到呢刻我order左碗粉&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n之後肥仔老闆開始發表偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好明顯佢真係唔識架！話送中未發生過班人唔知驚乜，警察一早應該出實彈鎮壓，唔可以比人成日示威抗議，之後電視影到出水炮車佢拍手叫好，係咁叫快d射低班暴徒，另一個阿叔話示威者收哂錢，咁鍾意破壞應該捉哂全部去黑龍江揼石仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肥仔又話要望實水炮車射人精彩一刻唔可以錯過。<br />\n<br />\n我都知我好廢無當場反枱仲比錢佢賺，但係當時我一個女人佢地幾個阿叔可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心痛出去搏命嘅義士比佢地不停話，唯一做到只有公開佢，比大家思考下仲要唔要幫襯，我呢世都唔會再入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，佢啲麵都幾撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華富村華安樓地下投注站側邊嗰間呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"末有反送中食過幾次 知道佢係藍色以後都唔會再食"},{"pid":"863e892f28e49c6485d210538076fdc3367f3dae","tid":1505212,"uid":159760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a4da0088c880284cad7b9ebc2e8bebd628de1e","tid":1505212,"uid":35758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c3abd1461bc704ec659d4ee9cac6249e6204806","tid":1505212,"uid":258893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"華富係深籃老人邨，後生既搬走哂。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"係深藍民主黨就唔會喺二邨做到成20年<br />\n下邨上次都係差少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"差個幾票就踢走歐立成"},{"pid":"70fbb45ef5720e4b910f67ec5b0dd66a857a6996","tid":1505212,"uid":34367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢黑店嚟"},{"pid":"cf3e41a1c6127054157a19a2b337d1a7d0d43bb9","tid":1505212,"uid":131017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"863e892f28e49c6485d210538076fdc3367f3dae","tid":1505212,"uid":159760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a4da0088c880284cad7b9ebc2e8bebd628de1e","tid":1505212,"uid":35758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c3abd1461bc704ec659d4ee9cac6249e6204806","tid":1505212,"uid":258893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:40:49.000Z","